history.content:
I'm currently on the waitlist for EECS 127, and it was supposed to allow time conflict enrollment (mentioned this when I added it to my schedule). The discussion section I've chosen for it conflicts with a section for another class I'm enrolled in.

However I got an email yesterday saying that I cannot be enrolled in 127 until I resolve the time conflict. I tried changing my discussion section for 127 by going through the 'Options' button, but it won't let me change my section as I'm not enrolled in the course yet. I cannot change the section for the other class since there are no open seats in any other discussion section.

What can I do in this situation? I don't want to drop 127 and enroll again because I'm on waitlist number 6, and there is a total waitlist of 34 people now. I've emailed Cal Student Central, but I wanted to post here as well in case someone has resolved an issue like this before. Thanks!
history.subject: Changing discussion section for waitlisted class
